import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt  
lyricdf=pd.read_excel('/Users/anna/Desktop/PRISMOJI/chancelyrics.xlsx', 
                     sheetname="all_lyrics")
lyricdf['Release_Date'] =pd.to_datetime(lyricdf.Release_Date)
igh=lyricdf['Lyrics'].str.count('igh')
lyricdf['igh_count']=igh
god=lyricdf['Lyrics'].str.count('God')
lyricdf['god_count']=god
blessing=lyricdf['Lyrics'].str.count('blessing')
lyricdf['blessing_count']=blessing
lyricdf

ighdf=lyricdf.drop(["Song", "Release_Date", "Lyrics", "blessing_count", "god_count"], axis=1)
albumigh=ighdf['igh_count'].groupby(ighdf['Album']).sum()
albumigh=pd.DataFrame(albumigh).reset_index()
albumigh

import seaborn as sns
sns.set_style('white')
ax=sns.factorplot(x='igh_count', y ='Album', data=albumigh.sort_values('igh_count', ascending = False), kind='bar', size=4, aspect=1.75, 
                  color="red", alpha=0.8)
plt.title('Igh Per Album')
ax.set(xlabel="Frequency", ylabel="Album")

plt.show()

from nltk import sent_tokenize, word_tokenize, pos_tag
import re
import string
from nltk.corpus import stopwords
punctuation = list(string.punctuation)
stops=set(stopwords.words('english')+punctuation)
lyricwords=str(lyricdf.Lyrics.unique())
lyricwords=re.sub(r"(?<![A-Z])(?<!^)([A-Z])",r" \1",lyricwords)
lyricwords=lyricwords.replace("\'", "").replace("\\", "").replace("\n ", "")
lyricwords=lyricwords.lower()
words=word_tokenize(lyricwords)
words=[word for word in words if word not in punctuation]
words=[word for word in words if word not in stops]
wordseries=pd.Series(words).value_counts()
worddf=pd.DataFrame(wordseries)
worddf=worddf.drop("''")
worddf=worddf.reset_index()
worddf.columns=["Word", "Count"]
worddf

def find_bigrams(words):
  bigram_list = []
  for i in range(len(words)-1):
      bigram_list.append((words[i], words[i+1]))
  return bigram_list

import numpy as np
gtrends=pd.merge(chancenews, chancesearch)
gtrends.columns=["Date", "Mentions", "Searches"]
trends = gigs.merge(gtrends, how='outer')
trends["Date"]=pd.to_datetime(trends.Date)
trends["Date"]=trends["Date"].dt.strftime('%Y-%m')
trends=trends.sort_values("Date")
trends=trends.set_index("Date")
trends.columns=["Gigs", "Google News Mentions", "Google Searches"]
ew=pd.ewma(trends, span=25, how='sum')
ew["Gigs"]=[num*2.85 for num in ew["Gigs"]]
ew["Google News Mentions"]=[num*2.94 for num in ew["Google News Mentions"]]
ew["Google Searches"]=[num*2.94 for num in ew["Google Searches"]]
ew.plot.area(lw=2, alpha=0.4, stacked=False)
plt.style.use(['fivethirtyeight', 'seaborn-darkgrid'])
plt.legend(loc='upper left', fontsize=10)
plt.yticks(fontsize=10, color="dimgrey")
plt.xticks(fontsize=10, color="dimgrey")
plt.xlabel("Date", fontsize=12, color="dimgrey")
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 14))
plt.show()
trends.plot.area(stacked=False)
